Class ValuedProperty

java.lang.Object
  eu.threecixty.privacy.datastorage.ValuedProperty

public final class ValuedProperty
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a property of the profile with all these values depending on the fact that the property is mono-value or multi-values. It is intended that a property could have several identical values
